<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>HOSPITAL LABYRINTH: THE FACE OF FEAR v11</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; background: #000; overflow: hidden; font-family: 'Courier New', sans-serif; user-select: none; }
        #canvas-container { width: 100vw; height: 100vh; }
        
        .glitch-active { animation: shake 0.1s infinite alternate; }
        @keyframes shake {
            0% { transform: translate(3px, 2px) rotate(0deg); filter: contrast(1.5) brightness(1.2); }
            100% { transform: translate(-3px, -2px) rotate(0.5deg); filter: contrast(1.0) brightness(0.7); }
        }

        .blackout-glitch { animation: blackout-spark 0.08s infinite alternate; }
        @keyframes blackout-spark {
            0% { opacity: 0.1; filter: invert(0); }
            100% { opacity: 0.9; filter: invert(0.05) brightness(0.3); }
        }

        #ui-layer {
            position: absolute; top: 20px; left: 20px; 
            color: #fff; background: rgba(5, 8, 6, 0.96); 
            padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; border: 2px solid #ff3333;
            font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        #floor-display { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #ff3333; text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ff0000; }
        
        #stamina-container {
            position: absolute; bottom: 30px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 300px; height: 10px; background: rgba(34, 34, 34, 0.7); 
            border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 5px; overflow: hidden; z-index: 180;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); pointer-events: none;
        }
        #stamina-bar { width: 100%; height: 100%; background: #00ffaa; transition: width 0.05s linear; }

        /* アイテムUI */
        #item-ui-container {
            position: absolute; bottom: 30px; left: 30px;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.85); border: 2px solid #00ffaa;
            padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; color: white; font-size: 13px;
            z-index: 180; width: 220px; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,255,170,0.3);
        }
        .status-active { color: #ff0055; font-weight: bold; animation: pulse 0.5s infinite alternate; }
        .status-buff { color: #00ffaa; font-weight: bold; }

        #start-screen {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: #020202; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column; z-index: 300; color: white; text-align: center;
        }
        #screen-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-direction: column;
            z-index: 200; display: none; text-shadow: 0 0 10px #000; color: white; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
        }
        .btn { margin-top:20px; padding:12px 30px; font-size:18px; cursor:pointer; background:#111; color:#ff3333; border:2px solid #ff3333; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .btn:hover { background:#ff3333; color:#000; box-shadow: 0 0 15px #ff3333; }
        
        /* ミニマップコンテナ（通常時と拡大時をCSSクラスで制御） */
        #minimap-container {
            position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px;
            width: 180px; height: 180px; 
            background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.98);
            border: 2px solid #ff3333;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 150;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.6), inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }
        #minimap-container.large {
            top: 50%; right: 50%;
            transform: translate(50%, -50%);
            width: 450px; height: 450px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.9), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            z-index: 220;
        }
        #minimap { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }

        #diary-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.97); display: none; justify-content: center;
            align-items: center; flex-direction: column; z-index: 250;
        }
        #diary-box {
            background: #070707; border: 2px solid #ffaa00; padding: 35px;
            max-width: 550px; width: 80%; border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 170, 0, 0.3); line-height: 2.0;
            font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', 'MS Mincho', serif;
        }
        #diary-content { white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 16px; color: #eddcc4; letter-spacing: 1.5px; }
        
        #guide-notice {
            position: absolute; bottom: 60px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #ffaa44; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; z-index: 100; text-align: center; 
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #ffaa44;
            letter-spacing: 1px; pointer-events: none;
        }

        #yusei-alert {
            position: absolute; bottom: 110px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #ff2200; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; z-index: 110; text-align: center;
            background: rgba(10, 0, 0, 0.95); padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 4px; border: 2px solid #ff2200;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.7); display: none;
            animation: pulse 0.6s infinite alternate; pointer-events: none;
        }
        @keyframes pulse { from { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(0.96); } to { opacity: 1.0; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.04); } }

        #chaser-speech-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 40%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #ff0000; 
            font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', 'MS Mincho', 'Zapfino', serif;
            font-size: 56px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 15px; z-index: 220;
            pointer-events: none; display: none; text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #220000, -3px -3px 0px #000, 0 0 20px #ff0000, 0 0 40px #550000, 0 0 60px #000000;
            animation: horrorGlitchText 0.12s infinite alternate;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        @keyframes horrorGlitchText {
            0% { transform: translate(-53%, -48%) scale(0.95) skewX(-6deg); filter: blur(1px); }
            50% { transform: translate(-48%, -52%) scale(1.03) skewX(4deg); filter: blur(0px); }
            100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.0) skewX(-2deg); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px red); }
        }

        #jumpscare-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
            background: #000; z-index: 500; display: none;
            justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow: hidden;
        }
        #jumpscare-canvas {
            width: 100vh; height: 100vh;
            animation: jumpscare-glitch 0.04s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes jumpscare-glitch {
            0% { transform: scale(1.15) translate(10px, -10px) rotate(1deg); filter: contrast(4.0) brightness(1.8); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.3) translate(-8px, 4px) rotate(-1deg); filter: invert(0.05) contrast(4.5); }
            100% { transform: scale(1.4) translate(-12px, 12px) rotate(-1deg); filter: contrast(5.0) brightness(2.2); }
        }

        #hiding-prompt {
            position: absolute; top: 60%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; z-index: 190; text-align: center;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); padding: 10px 25px; border-radius: 5px; border: 2px solid #00ffaa;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.5); display: none; pointer-events: none;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        #hiding-vision-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
            background: #000000; z-index: 140; display: none; pointer-events: none;
        }
        #slit-window {
            position: absolute; top: 15%; left: 46%; width: 8%; height: 70%;
            border-left: 4px solid #1a1a1a; border-right: 4px solid #1a1a1a;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.95), 0 0 50px rgba(0,0,0,1);
            background: transparent;
        }

        /* 血の脈動ビネット（接近時） */
        #vignette-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none; z-index: 130;
        }
        #vignette-overlay.danger { animation: vignettePulse 0.55s infinite alternate; }
        @keyframes vignettePulse {
            0%  { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 40%, rgba(180,0,0,0.0) 60%, rgba(180,0,0,0.5) 100%); }
            100%{ background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, transparent 40%, rgba(180,0,0,0.2) 65%, rgba(180,0,0,0.95) 100%); }
        }
        .blood-text {
            position: absolute; color: #8b0000; font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN','MS Mincho',serif;
            font-size: 30px; font-weight: 900; pointer-events: none; z-index: 132;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px #ff0000, 2px 2px 0 #000;
            animation: bloodFade 5s ease-in-out forwards;
            letter-spacing: 4px; opacity: 0;
        }
        @keyframes bloodFade {
            0%   { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px) scale(0.93); filter: blur(4px); }
            18%  { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(0px) scale(1.0); filter: blur(0px); }
            75%  { opacity: 0.75; }
            100% { opacity: 0; }
        }
        #face-flash-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none; z-index: 135; display: none;
            justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }
        #face-flash-canvas {
            width: 70vh; height: 70vh;
            animation: faceFlashAnim 0.5s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes faceFlashAnim {
            0%   { opacity: 0; transform: scale(2.2); filter: contrast(3) blur(8px); }
            25%  { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.08); filter: contrast(4) blur(0px); }
            80%  { opacity: 0.8; }
            100% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.88); }
        }
        #eye-glow-left, #eye-glow-right {
            position: absolute; top: 42%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 134; display: none;
        }
        #eye-glow-left  { left: 0px; }
        #eye-glow-right { right: 0px; }
        .eye-glow-canvas { animation: eyeGlowPulse 0.75s infinite alternate; }
        @keyframes eyeGlowPulse {
            0%  { opacity: 0.3; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px #ff0000) brightness(0.6); }
            100%{ opacity: 1.0; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 22px #ff2200) brightness(1.4); }
        }
        #glitch-lines-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none; z-index: 133; display: none; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .glitch-line {
            position: absolute; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 2px;
            background: rgba(255,0,0,0.65); mix-blend-mode: screen;
            animation: glitchLineFade 0.2s forwards;
        }
        @keyframes glitchLineFade {
            0%  { opacity: 1; }
            100%{ opacity: 0; transform: translateX(60px); }
        }

        /* タイピング解錠UI */
        #typing-lock-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95); display: none; justify-content: center;
            align-items: center; flex-direction: column; z-index: 260;
        }
        #typing-lock-box {
            background: #060606; border: 2px solid #ffcc00;
            padding: 40px; max-width: 600px; width: 85%; border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,180,0,0.4), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            text-align: center; font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN','MS Mincho',serif;
        }
        #typing-lock-title {
            color: #ffcc00; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 12px #ffaa00;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        #typing-lock-prompt {
            color: #cc9900; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
        }
        #typing-lock-phrase {
            color: #ffee88; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 18px;
            letter-spacing: 2px; background: rgba(40,30,0,0.6);
            padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #665500;
            min-height: 2em; line-height: 1.6;
        }
        #typing-lock-input {
            background: #0a0a0a; border: 2px solid #666; color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 4px; width: 90%;
            font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN','MS Mincho',serif;
            outline: none; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        #typing-lock-input:focus { border-color: #ffcc00; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,200,0,0.3); }
        #typing-lock-input.correct { border-color: #00ff88; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,255,100,0.5); color: #00ff88; }
        #typing-lock-input.wrong { border-color: #ff2200; animation: wrongShake 0.3s ease; }
        @keyframes wrongShake {
            0%,100%{ transform: translateX(0); } 20%{ transform: translateX(-8px); } 60%{ transform: translateX(8px); }
        }
        #typing-lock-progress {
            color: #888; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        #typing-lock-progress span { color: #ffcc00; font-weight: bold; }
        #typing-lock-hint {
            color: #555; font-size: 11px; margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* タイピング解錠UI */
        #typing-lock-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95); display: none; justify-content: center;
            align-items: center; flex-direction: column; z-index: 260;
        }
        #typing-lock-box {
            background: #060606; border: 2px solid #ffcc00;
            padding: 40px; max-width: 600px; width: 85%; border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,180,0,0.4), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
            text-align: center; font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN','MS Mincho',serif;
        }
        #typing-lock-title {
            color: #ffcc00; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 12px #ffaa00;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
        #typing-lock-prompt {
            color: #cc9900; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
        }
        #typing-lock-phrase {
            color: #ffee88; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 18px;
            letter-spacing: 2px; background: rgba(40,30,0,0.6);
            padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #665500;
            min-height: 2em; line-height: 1.6;
        }
        #typing-lock-input {
            background: #0a0a0a; border: 2px solid #666; color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 4px; width: 90%;
            font-family: 'Hiragino Mincho ProN','MS Mincho',serif;
            outline: none; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        #typing-lock-input:focus { border-color: #ffcc00; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,200,0,0.3); }
        #typing-lock-input.correct { border-color: #00ff88; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,255,100,0.5); color: #00ff88; }
        #typing-lock-input.wrong { border-color: #ff2200; animation: wrongShake 0.3s ease; }
        @keyframes wrongShake {
            0%,100%{ transform: translateX(0); } 20%{ transform: translateX(-8px); } 60%{ transform: translateX(8px); }
        }
        #typing-lock-progress {
            color: #888; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        #typing-lock-progress span { color: #ffcc00; font-weight: bold; }
        #typing-lock-hint {
            color: #555; font-size: 11px; margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* タイマーUI */
        #timer-display {
            position: absolute; top: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #00ffaa; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 3px; z-index: 150; pointer-events: none;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px #00ffaa, 0 0 20px #00aa66;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); padding: 4px 18px; border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,170,0.3);
        }
        #timer-display.danger-time { color: #ff4400; text-shadow: 0 0 8px #ff4400; border-color: rgba(255,68,0,0.4); }
        /* ベストタイム記録表示 */
        #best-time-display {
            position: absolute; top: 58px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: #888; font-size: 12px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 2px; z-index: 150; pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* 隠れ中の扉引っかき跡 */
        #scratch-overlay {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none; z-index: 145; display: none;
        }
        .scratch-mark {
            position: absolute; width: 3px; border-radius: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(180,0,0,0.7), transparent);
            animation: scratchAppear 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes scratchAppear {
            0%  { transform: scaleY(0) translateY(-50%); opacity: 0; }
            30% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1); }
            100%{ opacity: 0.5; }
        }
        /* 日記取得赤フラッシュ */
        #diary-pickup-flash {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none; z-index: 136; display: none;
            background: rgba(200,0,0,0.75);
            animation: diaryFlash 0.4s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes diaryFlash {
            0%  { opacity: 1; }
            100%{ opacity: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body id="game-body">

    <div id="start-screen">
        <h1 style="color: #ff0000; font-size: 42px; letter-spacing: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px; text-shadow: 0 0 25px #ff0000;">廃病院の怪異：漆黒 扉の深淵</h1>
        <p style="color: #8a948f; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; letter-spacing: 1px;">画像同期恐怖再現版 v11 (アップデート完了)</p>
        <p style="color: #ccc; font-size: 14px; max-width: 650px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            【怪異・探索アップデート統合完了】<br>
            🗺️ <b>解放型ミニマップ：</b> 自分が歩いた場所の霧が晴れる解放システム。<b>[M]キー</b>長押しで中央に大表示！<br>
            👁️ <b>3階・田中チー牛の化け物襲来：</b> 提供された『image_a4b561.png』の歪んだ白き輪郭、非対称な漆黒の眼窩、剥き出しの歯を完全再現した怪異がクロセと共に牙を剥く。<br>
            📦 <b>家具の強化＆ランダムアイテム：</b> 棚やクローゼットの裏表グラフィックが進化。あけると加速・透明・そして偽物（デバフ罠）がランダム出現！
        </p>
        <button id="start-btn" class="btn">精神を刻み、潜入する</button>
    </div>

    <div id="ui-layer">
        <span id="floor-display">【現在位置: 廃病院 1階】</span><br>
        迷路の奥にある<span style="color:#ffff00;font-weight:bold;">「田中チー牛１１歳の日記（🟨）」</span>を回収し、<br>
        スタート地点（緑枠）まで生きて帰還せよ。<br><br>
        移動: <span style="color:#00ff00;font-weight:bold;">W, A, S, D</span> / 視点: <span style="color:#00ffff;font-weight:bold;">マウス</span><br>
        全力疾走: <span style="color:#ff3366;font-weight:bold;">Shiftキー長押し</span><br>
        マップ拡大: <span style="color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold;">Mキー長押し</span><br>
        懐中電灯ON/OFF: <span style="color:#ffcc00;font-weight:bold;">Qキー</span><br>
        家具の扉を開ける/閉める: <span style="color:#00ffaa;font-weight:bold;">Eキー</span><br>
        隠れる / 隠れ場所から出る: <span style="color:#ffff00;font-weight:bold;">Spaceキー</span>
    </div>

    <div id="stamina-container"><div id="stamina-bar"></div></div>
    <div id="timer-display">00:00.0</div>
    <div id="best-time-display"></div>
    
    <!-- アイテムステータスUI -->
    <div id="item-ui-container">
        <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #555; padding-bottom:5px; margin-bottom:5px; font-weight:bold; color:#00ffaa;">EQUIPMENT / STATUS</div>
        <div id="item-slot">所持アイテム: なし</div>
        <div id="status-effect" style="margin-top:5px; font-size:11px; color:#aaa;">状態異常: 正常</div>
    </div>

    <div id="guide-notice">【警告】定期的に非常灯も消える完全停電や、ライトの故障が発生する…！</div>
    <div id="yusei-alert">⚠️ 怪異が接近中！近くの隠れ場所に逃げ込め！</div>
    <div id="chaser-speech-overlay"></div>
    <div id="jumpscare-overlay"><canvas id="jumpscare-canvas"></canvas></div>
    
    <!-- ミニマップ -->
    <div id="minimap-container"><canvas id="minimap" width="450" height="450"></canvas></div>
    
    <div id="hiding-prompt"></div>
    <div id="hiding-vision-overlay"><div id="slit-window"></div></div>
    <div id="vignette-overlay"></div>
    <div id="glitch-lines-overlay"></div>
    <div id="face-flash-overlay"><canvas id="face-flash-canvas" width="600" height="600"></canvas></div>
    <div id="eye-glow-left"><canvas class="eye-glow-canvas" id="eye-canvas-left" width="100" height="50"></canvas></div>
    <div id="scratch-overlay"></div>
    <div id="diary-pickup-flash"></div>
    <div id="eye-glow-right"><canvas class="eye-glow-canvas" id="eye-canvas-right" width="100" height="50"></canvas></div>

    <!-- タイピング解錠UI -->
    <div id="typing-lock-overlay">
